    "id": "slide17",
    "eyebrow": "Knowledge Gaps",
    "num": "17",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">17</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Knowledge Gaps</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Questions Remaining About Bread Baking</h2><ul><li>Optimal kneading times for different flours?</li><li>Precise fermentation conditions for best flavor?</li><li>Effects of ingredient variations on texture?</li><li>Standardized troubleshooting protocols?</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Many practical questions remain unanswered due to limited research, highlighting areas for future study [s1]. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s1\">[1]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Uncertainty about how long to knead whole wheat flour dough.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> List questions you have about bread baking that need more evidence.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Assuming current knowledge is complete or universally applicable.</p></div></div>",
