    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">26</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Application</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Using Bread Baking Skills in Daily Cooking</h2><ul><li>Adapt ingredient knowledge to other recipes.</li><li>Apply fermentation understanding to new foods.</li><li>Use troubleshooting skills for cooking challenges.</li><li>Maintain critical evaluation of cooking advice.</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Bread baking skills enhance overall cooking competence and critical thinking [s1]. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s1\">[1]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Making homemade pizza dough using bread baking principles.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Identify a cooking task where you can apply bread baking skills.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Assuming all cooking processes are identical to bread baking.</p></div></div>"
